org.batfish.question

Class BgpLoopbacksQuestionPlugin.BgpLoopbacksQuestion

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.datamodel.questions.Question
      • org.batfish.question.BgpLoopbacksQuestionPlugin.BgpLoopbacksQuestion
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IQuestion
    Enclosing class:
    BgpLoopbacksQuestionPlugin

    public static class BgpLoopbacksQuestionPlugin.BgpLoopbacksQuestion
extends Question
    Lists which loopback interfaces are being announced into BGP.

    When running BGP without an IGP, one may wish to announce loopback interface IPs into BGP. This question produces the list of nodes for which such announcements are not happening.
